welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Gretna, the charming city known for its rich history and friendly locals. We invite you to explore and soak in all that Gretna has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lakefront Airport offers domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Lakefront Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

airports.airport_name: Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Louis Armstrong New Orléans International Airport houses all major airlines and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is a satellite terminal connected to the main terminal via a walkway. It primarily serves Southwest Airlines and offers a variety of dining and shopping options.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B is a satellite terminal connected to the main terminal via a walkway. It primarily serves Delta Airlines and offers a variety of dining and shopping options.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. Simply connect to the network and accept the terms and conditions.
